[PNG image data: 64x64 pixel art of a cyberpunk cityscape with neon lights, tall buildings, and a starry night sky. Created with a limited color palette featuring deep purples, electric blues, hot pinks, and bright yellows. The scene depicts a futuristic city with glowing windows, holographic billboards, and a crescent moon. The art style is intentionally retro with visible pixel grid, evoking nostalgia for classic 8-bit games while depicting a modern sci-fi theme. Chose this theme because cyberpunk aesthetics blend perfectly with pixel art's inherent limitations, turning constraints into creative strengths.]